Package Servletter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GenerateOrder
    This class is called from shopCart.jsp.
    GenerateOrderLine
    This class generates orderlines to the future order from shopCart.jsp and then redirects back to the same page, but now with an orderline attached to the page.
    Login_Registration
    This class is called from both index.jsp(login) and registration.jsp pages, where two differents forms are pushed.
    ViewGenerator
    This class is the "Render class" it takes alot of the work away from the jsp pages so they can look smooth.
